<inglise> COMMISSION REGULATION (EEC) No 2829/79 of 14 December 1979 amending Regulation (EEC) No 1963/79 laying down detailed rules for the application of the production refund on olive oil used in the manufacture of certain preserved foods </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (EM&Uuml;) nr 2829/79, millega muudetakse m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 1963/79, milles s&auml;testatakse teatavate konservide tootmisel kasutatava oliivi&otilde;li tootmistoetuse &uuml;ksikasjalikud rakenduseeskirjad 14. detsember 1979 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Economic Community, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa Majandus&uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation No 136/66/EEC of 22 September 1966 on the establishment of a common organization of the market in oils and fats (1), as last amended by Regulation (EEC) No 590/79 (2), </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 22. septembri 1966. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust nr 136/66/EM&Uuml; &otilde;li- ja rasvaturu &uuml;hise korralduse kehtestamise kohta, (1) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 590/79, (2) </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 591/79 of 26 March 1979 laying down general rules concerning the production refund for olive oils used in the manufacture of certain preserved foods (3), and in particular Article 9 thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 26. m&auml;rtsi 1979. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 591/79, millega n&auml;hakse ette teatavate konservide tootmisel kasutatava oliivi&otilde;li tootmistoetuse &uuml;ldeeskirjad, (3) eriti selle artiklit 9, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Article 2 (1) of Commission Regulation (EEC) No 1963/79 (4) provides that requests for the verification of oil must be submitted to the competent authority not later than five working days before the date envisaged for the commencement of the manufacture of the preserved foods in which it is to be used; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: komisjoni m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1963/79 (4) artikli 2 l&otilde;ikes 1 on s&auml;testatud, et taotlused &otilde;li kontrollimiseks tuleb p&auml;devale asutusele esitada nende konservide puhul, kus seda &otilde;li kasutatakse, hiljemalt viis t&ouml;&ouml;p&auml;eva enne tootmise alustamiseks kavandatud kuup&auml;eva; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the object of this fixed period is to permit verification of the stock of olive oil by the competent authority; whereas, since methods of carrying out this administrative check differ from one Member State to another, the Member States should themselves set the period which is necessary for them to carry out the check in question; </inglise>
<eesti> k&otilde;nealuse kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ratud ajavahemiku eesm&auml;rk on v&otilde;imaldada p&auml;deval asutusel kontrollida oliivi&otilde;li varusid; kuna k&otilde;nealuse halduskontrolli l&auml;biviimise viisid on liikmesriigiti erinevad, peaksid liikmesriigid ise m&auml;&auml;rama neile vajaliku ajavahemiku k&otilde;nealuse kontrolli l&auml;biviimiseks; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the measures provided for in this Regulation are in accordance with the opinion of the Management Committee for Oils and Fats, </inglise>
<eesti> k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;rusega etten&auml;htud meetmed on koosk&otilde;las &otilde;li- ja rasvaturu korralduskomitee arvamusega, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 (1) of Regulation (EEC) No 1963/79 is amended to read as follows: </inglise>
<eesti> M&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1963/79 artikli 2 l&otilde;ige 1 muudetakse j&auml;rgmiseks: </eesti>
<inglise> "1. </inglise>
<eesti> "1. </eesti>
<inglise> In order to qualify for the production refund, the manufacturer must submit a request for verification to the competent authority before the date envisaged for the commencement of manufacturing operations. </inglise>
<eesti> Tootmistoetuse saamiseks peab tootja esitama kontrollitaotluse p&auml;devale asutusele enne tootmistegevuse alustamiseks kavandatud kuup&auml;eva. </eesti>
<inglise> Such a request may not be submitted until the oil is in the manufacturing premises. </inglise>
<eesti> Seda taotlust ei v&otilde;i esitada enne, kui &otilde;li on tootmisettev&otilde;ttes. </eesti>
<inglise> The Member State concerned shall, if necessary, specify a minimum period which must elapse between the submission of the request for verification and the date specified in the first subparagraph. " </inglise>
<eesti> Asjaomased liikmesriigid t&auml;psustavad vajaduse korral minimaalse ajavahemiku, mis peab j&auml;&auml;ma kontrollitaotluse esitamise ja esimeses l&otilde;igus nimetatud kuup&auml;eva vahele." </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall enter into force on the third day following its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus j&otilde;ustub kolmandal p&auml;eval p&auml;rast selle avaldamist Euroopa &Uuml;henduste Teatajas. </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus on tervikuna siduv ja vahetult kohaldatav k&otilde;ikides liikmesriikides. </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Brussels, 14 December 1979. </inglise>
